	<h2>Plot</h2>
	<p>Pebble, a unique caterpillar made of pebbles, is determined to reach a green leaf</p>

	<div class="space"></div>

	<h2>Description</h2>
	<div class="halfpage">
		<div class="column1">
			<img src="/images/films/pebble/poster.webp">
		</div>
		<div class="column2">
			<p>This is our first short film and it's completely made with Blender.<br>
		The project itself started because we wanted to prove we were able to make a film from beginning to end, and while some assets were ready (like the trees from our Real Trees add-on), we still had to make the microscopic pebbles, leaves and other details in order to provide that touch of realism that we based the film on.<br>
		We are willing to make more of them in the future.</p>
